article.title: Galaxy Developer Roundtable
article.tease: Tool testing and tool deployment discussion
article.contact: Dannon Baker, John Chilton, Marius van den Beek
article.content:
Super informal meeting this week including a discussion of tool testing and tool deployment issues.

Please join us at Noon, US Eastern time (see in your timezone).

Have something you want to talk about at a future roundtable? Submit your topic here.

The Galaxy Developer Roundatble meets every other Thursday as long as there are one or more presenters signed up for the week. These gatherings are an opportunity for presenters (Galaxy users, developers, admins) to interactively engage with the Galaxy developer community.
